vulnerability.name: USN-5401-1
vulnerability.description: Wenxiang Qian discovered that DPDK incorrectly checked certain payloads. An attacker could use this issue to cause DPDK to crash, resulting in a denial of service, or possibly execute arbitrary code. (CVE-2021-3839)  It was discovered that DPDK incorrectly handled inflight type messages. An attacker could possibly use this issue to cause DPDK to consume resources, leading to a denial of service. (CVE-2022-0669)

statements.status_notes: Several security issues were fixed in DPDK.
